    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is beginning to soften, add your<strong> arborio rice</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the oil</p><p>Add your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and cook for a further 30 secs or until it has evaporated, then reduce the heat to medium-low</p>",
