    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the risotto is cooking, roll your<strong> lemon[s] </strong>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1721725779629-x200.jpg",
