      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once your risotto has absorbed all the stock, remove the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>risotto </strong>from the heat and stir in the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> and a generous knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Season very generously with <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>lemon and saffron risotto</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if the risotto is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
