      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lemon and saffron risotto</strong> topped with a handful of<strong> salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> salad</strong> with a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>sea bass</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
